    <refsection xml:id="Description_Integer_pal">
        <title>Description</title>
        <para>
            That palette is dedicated to handle integer numbers. Various basic
            operators for the management of bit fields and for logic are implemented
            as well as common gates encountered in digital circuits.
        </para>
